The interfaith community paid its tributes to the late Anglican Archbishop Emeritus Desmond Mpilo Tutu this week. Let’s take a look at some of these moving tributes. Courtesy #DStv403 CAPE TOWN - The interfaith community paid its tributes to the late Anglican Archbishop Emeritus Desmond Mpilo Tutu this week. Tutu passed away on Sunday at the age of 90. WATCH: Remembering Archbishop Emeritus Desmond Tutu Tutu has been described as a great and influential man by many who paid tribute to him. He will be laid to rest in Cape Town on Saturday.